{"name":"仪表盘支持「透视表」组件了","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"IMG_KEY_TODO","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","corner_radius":"8px","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":":Loudspeaker: **<font color='green'>自由拖拽，灵活汇总，让数据分析更高效</font>**\n- **销售分析：** 按人员、区域、时间等维度交叉汇总销售数据，识别高绩效区域与增长机会\n- **采购统计：** 分供应商、物料、月份统计采购金额与到货率，辅助成本控制与采购策略调整\n- **营销活动效果分析：** 分活动、渠道、时间维度统计曝光、点击、转化，衡量投放成效","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":":StatusFlashOfInspiration: **除此之外：**\n支持基于透视表直接 **「生成数据表」**。这突破了透视表组件的限制，让你能够在汇总数据的基础上，无缝衔接公式计算、自动化流程、搭建图表等能力，最大化数据价值。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"帮助文档"},"type":"primary","width":"default","size":"medium","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"file-link-docx_outlined"},"behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/377639339118-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E8%A1%A8%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6#tabs0|ttd8aOwdr9","pc_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/377639339118-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E8%A1%A8%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6#tabs0|ttd8aOwdr9","ios_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/377639339118-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E8%A1%A8%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6#tabs0|ttd8aOwdr9","android_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/377639339118-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E8%A1%A8%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6#tabs0|ttd8aOwdr9"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}]},"header":{"title":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"仪表盘支持「透视表」组件啦 "},"subtitle":{"tag":"plain_text","content":""},"text_tag_list":[{"tag":"text_tag","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"功能上新"},"color":"green"}],"template":"blue","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px"}},"variables":[]}